[[Translation:Main/en/Regional Investigator]]
{{en/-}}
The '''Regional Investigator''' is a government official who investigates improper or unethical behavior in business and provides oversight of the [[Main/en/Local Authority|local authorities]]. If he catches a [[Main/en/Transport Company|transport company]] [[Main/en/Local Authority#Pass a Bribe|bribing a local authority]], he will block that company's services for that area for six months, and prevent further interaction with that Local Authority.
